{"id":148556,"type":6,"name":"香帥傳奇","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e0/01/148556_gyhY1.jpg","summary":"　　本剧根据古龙名著《楚留香传奇》改编而成。 \r\n　　洛阳城内，大捕头莫言飞檐走壁登上城墙，贴上告示捉拿采花大盗楚留香（郑少秋 饰），悬赏十万两黄金。被认为是采花大盗的楚留香蒙此不白之冤自然是不服气，毅然决意亲自追查真凶。孰料此乃诱楚留香重出江湖之计，意在委托楚留香追查被窃之佛祖舍利之下落。相传此舍利子为秦始皇专用，原存于皇陵。后楚留香与司空摘星闯迷宫，深入大漠，直到到波斯达里亚斯国，又纠缠于日月神教。一场尔虞我诈的家族争斗，一曲欲罢不能的爱情绝唱就此展开。楚留香几经生死，终于在中原少林寺歼灭大奸昭明太子.....","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>香帅传奇</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16494\">鄭少秋</a> / <a href=\"/person/17128\">楊麗菁</a> / 夏光莉 / <a href=\"/person/19763\">沈孟生</a> / <a href=\"/person/19765\">康凱</a> / <a href=\"/person/19764\">林美貞</a> / <a href=\"/person/19762\">陳亞蘭</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>27</li><li><span>开始: </span>1995-04-03</li><li><span>类型: </span>武侠 / 古装</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台湾</li><li><span>电视台: </span>台湾台视</li><li><span>导演: </span>范秀明</li><li><span>制片人/制作人: </span>曹景德</li><li><span>编剧: </span>刘麒</li><li><span>监制: </span>顾安生</li>","collection":{"collect":2},"eps":[{"id":573054,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573054","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573055,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573055","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573056,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573056","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573057,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573057","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573058,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573058","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573059,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573059","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":573060,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/573060","type":0,"sort":7,"name